        <skos:definition rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The food environment is the community-level physical, economic, political, and sociocultural conditions that impact the interface(s) where people acquire and consume food, shaping dietary behaviors and health.</skos:definition>
